React
- library from facebook team
- think in component (smallest thing)
- render funtion return only one element(include inner element) and fully close
- properties -> passing value into another element
States 
- data in its component(like a props but avaiable only component)
- method of calling is the same of propertiy
React Lifecycle
- componentWillMount
- componentDidMount
- shoukdComponentUpdate
- componentWillUnmount
- render (!!!)

How to start
- create package.json (manage dependency)
- create webpack.config.json (pack into one file)
- create .babelrc (convert es6 to es5)
 
